short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A Chrome extension that deduplicates open tabs

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension provides a feature to resolve duplication in open tabs.
When you're opening a lot of tabs, tabs are easy to be open duplicatedly without knowing, and it's bothering a bit to resolve it by hand.
By using this extension, you can do that by 1 click.
